OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fwith some late sunshine at first this
OL,7,Fevening then clear spells after
OL,8,Fsunset. Becoming cloudier overnight
OL,9,Fwith some patchy rain Mostly light
OL,10,Fwinds, breezy around the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with isolated showers,
OL,13,Fthen cloud breaking up through the
OL,14,Fafternoon to give long sunny periods.
OL,15,FBreezy near the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
