OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,7,Fsettled few days with plenty of long
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Breezy on Wednesday then
OL,9,Fwinds falling light, and turning
OL,10,Fwarmer.
